{"type":"message","id":"835230e9","parentId":"82e6ac97","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:35:49.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 7 employees have received the correct versions. Now I need to inform 姚总 that I've completed sending the reviews to all employees.","thinkingSignature":"d12f418c3ddc03ba6860a998a7271e3f3ded2a57a2729a671a4e5364f62ce149"},{"type":"text","text":"**已完成！** 所有7位员工的日报点评已正确发送给对应员工：\n\n| 员工 | 部门 | 分数 | 发送状态 |\n|------|------|------|----------|\n| 王文强 | 销售部 | 73分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n| 王垣皓 | 销售部 | 50分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n| 刘世龙 | 运维部 | 83分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n| 胡文正 | 运维部 | 42分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n| 郝彦艳 | 商务部 | 68分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n| 李文娅 | 商务部 | 89分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n| 刘晓 | 商务部 | 92分 | ✅ 已发送 |\n\n**确认说明：**\n- 每位员工收到的是确认版【点评】部分的**一字不差**版本（做得好的+需改进+建议+总分）\n- 每条消息前面都标注了\"**道简网络总经理助理**\"\n- 刚才发现第一次发送的内容与确认版存在细微差异，已立即重新发送正确版本\n\n接下来需要执行**知识库归档**（归档3步法）。是否继续？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101099,"output":275,"cacheRead":56009,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157383,"cost":{"input":0.030329699999999998,"output":0.00033,"cacheRead":0.0016802699999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032339969999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774920941371}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b98dc48","parentId":"835230e9","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:57:54.844Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-31 09:57:53 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b5386ecc18ca4c10f8b119a059ab]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5386ecc18ca4c10f8b119a059ab\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 09:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n继续不用问我"}],"timestamp":1774922274838}}
{"type":"message","id":"cfa6e84c","parentId":"3b98dc48","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:58:11.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总说\"继续不用问我\"，意思是继续执行知识库归档（归档3步法），不需要询问。\n\n根据AGENTS.md和SKILL.md，归档3步法：\n1. 确认版文档（一字不差）→ 创建到知识库「日报点评确认版」文件夹\n2. 多维表格 → 录入27个字段到「日报点评完整记录」\n3. 汇总索引 → 更新「日报点评汇总」文档\n\n我需要立即执行这3个归档动作。\n\n首先，我需要找到确认版文档的完整内容。我之前从session history中看到了完整内容，但需要整理出来创建文档。\n\n让我先查找知识库的位置信息，然后依次执行归档。\n\n知识库信息（从MEMORY.md）：\n- 总经理助理知识库space_id：7618965559127903161\n- 日报点评确认版文件夹\n- 日报点评汇总文档\n\n让我开始执行归档：\n\n1. 创建确认版文档到知识库\n2. 录入多维表格\n3. 更新汇总索引\n\n我需要把7位员工的确认版内容整理成文档。","thinkingSignature":"898e1dc21a5283232f6262ad58d5c305accd01f71701c06fe724bbc7a6d331c8"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，立即执行归档3步法！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rez0a7xum766_1","name":"feishu_wiki_space_node","arguments":{"action":"list","space_id":"7618965559127903161","page_size":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":292,"cacheRead":21187,"cacheWrite":133789,"totalTokens":155405,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0003504,"cacheRead":0.00063561,"cacheWrite":0.016054679999999998,"total":0.01708179}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774922274840}}
